title: Woman in the Shadows (1934) FAYE WRAY

sources.title: Woman in the Shadows (1934) FAYE WRAY
sources.description:
Stars: Fay Wray, Ralph Bellamy, Melvyn Douglas
Director: Phil Rosen
Writer: Dashiell Hammett (story)

Released from prison on parole, a man lives quietly in a cabin in the country, and then a beautiful disheveled woman in evening dress bursts in.... It's a Dahiell Hammett story so watch it !
